{"tid":2345202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔係拜登粉但係1月6日點睇都係雷聲大雨點小","createTime":"2020-12-29T10:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T15:29:29.000Z","uid":130385,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96f4008b8ba23b7bde1e177283364195458e6b76","tid":2345202,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家d人又吹1月6日承認侵侵d票之後獲得3xx票  勝爆<br />\n理論上係咁無錯  但係同軍事法庭單野都係一樣  敢講唔敢做<br />\n左顧右顧   依家好似連左膠的心情都要照顧埋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家侵侵班哂馬1月6日叫人出黎支持佢   個個期待當日戲劇式反敗為勝<br />\n但係跟據過往經驗 果日彭斯會宣佈拜登獲勝  原因係程序正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出貓都好比拜登做左先算   <br />\n之後就開始吹1月20日唔會落台永不放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但1月20日就正式落台比你睇<br />\n因為唔想做壞規矩  話會係民間繼續抗爭 永不放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c38df7f702f40e34f55899db1fbbdd9dace9384","tid":2345202,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeab5d179f8eaf7ccc629c733e917c56d27f224","tid":2345202,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"愛侵力準備入嚟<br />\n樓主快啲走<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/stop_medicine_argue_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae4d2c8ca5e218deabb95d4d0f3fc1b5aa5c3f4","tid":2345202,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"成件事最後咪又係1月20日拜登就職,<br />\n香港人生活不變, 繼續返工<br />\n唔明諗咁多做乜"},{"pid":"13f5fa2d50e566269d7f89525eca58721c045320","tid":2345202,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:20:12.000Z","msg":"美軍突襲cia <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse